OL,3,C'High value' candelabra stolen from
OL,4,CWelsh castle as police launch manhunt
OL,6,FSouth Wales Police have confirmed they
OL,7,Fare investigating a theft of a
OL,8,Fcandelabra from Cyfarthfa Castle.
OL,10,FThe force said it received a report on
OL,11,FTuesday, April 8, of the theft of the
OL,12,Fhistoric item from a display at the
OL,13,Fcastle.
OL,15,FNeighbourhood Inspector Meirion
OL,16,FCollings said: "The candelabra was a
OL,17,Fvaluable artefact and reuniting it to
OL,18,Fits rightful place will restore a part
OL,19,Fof the castle's heritage
