OL,6,F"It's important to acknowledge the
OL,7,Femotional impact of such incidents,
OL,8,Fespecially on the young visitors and
OL,9,Fstaff who were there at the time, and
OL,10,FI appreciate that it must have been an
OL,11,Fawful experience for them to have gone
OL,12,Fthrough and witness.
OL,14,F"Inquiries are continuing including
OL,15,Fthe viewing of CCTV footage and
OL,16,Fspeaking with witnesses as part of the
OL,17,Fongoing investigation and efforts to
OL,18,Frecover the artefact."
