OL,3,C'High value' candelabra stolen from
OL,4,CWelsh castle as police launch manhunt
OL,6,FThe police have now released images of
OL,7,Fa suspect they would like to speak to
OL,8,Fregarding the theft.
OL,10,FDetective Inspector Anthony Watts
OL,11,Fadded: "Our inquiries have established
OL,12,Fthat the suspect drove a silver Ford
OL,13,FFiesta Zetec which doesn't have any
OL,14,Fnumber plates attached to the front or
OL,15,Frear of the car.
OL,17,F"We are continuing to appeal for
OL,18,Finformation, and I would urge anyone
OL,19,Fwho may have seen anything suspicious
OL,20,Fin the days leading up to the theft to
OL,21,Fcontact us as soon as possible.
